{"tid":1385360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"8月5 三罷既咁做先有用.....","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:40:59.000Z","uid":164792,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"913b65043c8c59da9dca4b7fb4d8718e46ca4cfc","tid":1385360,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:13:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[我哋都唔想 要怪怪政府</span>repeat~repeat<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[我哋都唔想 要怪怪政府</span>repeat~repeat<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[我哋都唔想 要怪怪政府</span>repeat~repeat<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[我哋都唔想 要怪怪政府</span>repeat~repeat<br />\n<br />\n今日既試水溫<br />\n我地都知有打工仔係體諒我哋<br />\n<br />\n但係心理作用影響下 人一煩躁 有啲打工仔就算之前支持我地 佢哋都會直接怪左落我地身上人一亂就好中意搵藉口 所以我哋要提醒佢哋我哋 今日咁做係政權迫出嚟<br />\n要怪 怪政府 政府肯回應我哋當然唔會咁做<br />\n<br />\n錯誤做法:罷工&gt;打工仔嬲&gt;我地對唔住&gt;怪我地<br />\n<br />\n正確做法:罷工&gt;打工仔嬲&gt;要怪怪政府&gt;打工仔叮一聲，係bo 係政府唔回應<br />\n<br />\n人好易會墮入邏輯謬誤，所以我地提翻醒佢地"},{"pid":"58e1b7f07cfb8daa7caf077d6c70bfdc301345b5","tid":1385360,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"1f8fd9be2bbad6ade8c9f3e9c26fd7101a97960f","tid":1385360,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:13:19.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"531d67f04d6b7b819f3cef4ac7121a014598ca72","tid":1385360,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"ea0354c1a78c2c912876666a120ff4ba5b0540f2","tid":1385360,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:13:41.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"0c8f0d9f880e98a8404d0b11fb4e2c5c97df8c51","tid":1385360,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:13:53.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"0dd3ef46b86230bcd01f68887212a2861ba2eaa1","tid":1385360,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:14:47.000Z","msg":"對得住前線！對得住義士！<br />\n一日政府無回應 一日都要繼續抗爭！<br />\n一個都不能少！<br />\n堅持五大訴求！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c2132e515d2a0e16eaf2756ce6416e67a14d9e91","tid":1385360,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"1b63ec234b166a975961ae4ade669b3637b1f3b5","tid":1385360,"uid":120123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:17:43.000Z","msg":"班友識叮一聲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953078265cc06119597e2d8b177c0fb76cded7c7","tid":1385360,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"db0f9280c70faef1e780196e624d4433f9479138","tid":1385360,"uid":109794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:18:16.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!!<br />\nBTW<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請入 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsPmtT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsPmtT</a> 幫手推post!!<br />\n一齊report 9 藍絲 fb pages, 斷佢地輿論!!!!!<br />\n一人一Report, 搞到佢地摺埋!!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"beced15e8801af712ab2a59095b5fa1758e3595f","tid":1385360,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:18:24.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"1a1b16db57f438f5860419b20e642a37ff2a644d","tid":1385360,"uid":164792,"like":0